---
import RootLayout from '../../layouts/RootLayout.astro';
---

<RootLayout 
	title="About NOZA LLC - Digital Marketing & Web Design in Lexington, KY" 
	description="Learn about NOZA LLC, a founder-driven digital marketing and web design agency serving small businesses in Lexington and Central Kentucky."
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="about-hero">
		<div class="cosmic-background">
			<div class="stars"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-1"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-2"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-3"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="particles"></div>

		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1 class="about-headline">About NOZA LLC</h1>
			<p class="about-subheadline">A Lexington-based digital agency built for small business success. Founder-driven, client-obsessed, and deeply rooted in Central Kentucky.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Mission Section -->
	<section class="mission-section">
		<div class="mission-container">
			<div class="mission-grid">
				<div class="mission-card">
					<h2 class="mission-title">Our Mission</h2>
					<p class="mission-text">
						Empower Central Kentucky small businesses with digital solutions that drive real growth. We believe every business deserves access to world-class strategy, design, and marketing‚Äîregardless of size or budget.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="mission-card">
					<h2 class="mission-title">Our Values</h2>
					<ul class="values-list">
						<li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We tell the truth, even when it's not what you want to hear</li>
						<li><strong>Results:</strong> We're measured by outcomes, not billable hours</li>
						<li><strong>Partnership:</strong> Your success is our success</li>
						<li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We do excellent work or we don't do it</li>
						<li><strong>Local:</strong> Lexington and Central Kentucky matter to us</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Story Section -->
	<section class="story-section">
		<div class="story-container">
			<h2 class="story-title">Our Story</h2>
			<div class="story-content">
				<p>
					NOZA LLC was born from frustration. Our founder watched smart, capable entrepreneurs struggle with digital marketing and web design because existing agencies either didn't understand small business or charged prices that made no sense for early-stage ventures.
				</p>

				<p>
					The first project was simple: help a local contractor get better visibility online. It worked. More contractors called. Then service providers. Then retail businesses. Each one taught us something about what Central Kentucky small businesses actually need.
				</p>

				<p>
					What emerged wasn't a traditional agency. It was something different. A team that understands small business because we work closely with small businesses. That knows Lexington because we're from here. That's willing to have honest conversations about what will actually work versus what looks good in a proposal.
				</p>

				<p>
					Today, we serve dozens of Lexington and Central Kentucky businesses across web design, digital marketing, branding, photo/video, consulting, and networking. But the core philosophy hasn't changed: Do excellent work. Build real partnerships. Focus on outcomes, not hours. And remember that every client's success matters.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- What We Believe Section -->
	<section class="beliefs-section">
		<div class="beliefs-container">
			<h2 class="beliefs-title">What We Believe</h2>
			
			<div class="beliefs-grid">
				<div class="belief-item">
					<h3>Small Businesses are the Backbone</h3>
					<p>Central Kentucky's small businesses drive our economy and our culture. When local businesses thrive, our entire region thrives. We're invested in that success.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="belief-item">
					<h3>Strategy Beats Tactics</h3>
					<p>Anyone can design something pretty or post on social media. Real results come from clear strategy aligned with business goals. We focus on the big picture.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="belief-item">
					<h3>Technology Serves People</h3>
					<p>We use modern tools and frameworks, but never to overcomplicate things. Technology should make your life easier, not harder. We keep it real.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="belief-item">
					<h3>Relationships Matter</h3>
					<p>We're not transaction-focused. We build relationships that last. Your success becomes our responsibility. That's how we work.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="belief-item">
					<h3>Transparency is Non-Negotiable</h3>
					<p>You should always understand what we're doing, why we're doing it, and what results we're seeing. No jargon. No hidden fees. Just honesty.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="belief-item">
					<h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
					<p>Digital marketing and technology change constantly. We stay on top of trends, best practices, and new tools. Your business gets the benefit of our learning.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Team Section -->
	<section class="team-section">
		<div class="team-container">
			<h2 class="team-title">Who We Are</h2>
			<p class="team-subtitle">A team of experienced professionals who genuinely care about your success</p>

			<div class="team-info">
				<p>
					We're a lean, focused team. Not a massive agency with hundreds of people you'll never meet. That means you work directly with experienced professionals who understand your business and care about your outcomes.
				</p>
				<p>
					Our team brings experience from startups, agencies, in-house marketing departments, and consulting. We've worn every hat. That real-world experience means we understand the challenges you face and can offer practical solutions.
				</p>
				<p>
					But more than credentials and experience, our team is defined by genuine care. We're Lexington natives who want to see local businesses succeed. When you win, we celebrate with you. When challenges arise, we solve them together.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Process Section -->
	<section class="process-section">
		<div class="process-container">
			<h2 class="process-title">How We Work</h2>
			
			<div class="process-steps">
				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-icon">ü§ù</div>
					<h3>1. Partnership First</h3>
					<p>We're not vendors; we're partners in your growth. We care about understanding your business, your goals, and your constraints before we recommend anything.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-icon">üß†</div>
					<h3>2. Strategy Over Tactics</h3>
					<p>We build clear, coherent strategies before diving into execution. What's the goal? Who are we reaching? How will we measure success? These come first.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-icon">‚ú®</div>
					<h3>3. Excellent Execution</h3>
					<p>Once we're aligned on strategy, we execute with excellence. Clean code. Professional design. Thoughtful copy. Every detail matters because it reflects on you.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-icon">üìä</div>
					<h3>4. Measure & Optimize</h3>
					<p>We track what matters. Traffic. Leads. Sales. User behavior. Then we optimize based on real data. Always improving. Always learning.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-icon">üìû</div>
					<h3>5. Ongoing Partnership</h3>
					<p>Our relationship doesn't end at launch. We stay involved, keep improving, and adapt as your business evolves. You have a partner, not just a one-time service.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Service Area Section -->
	<section class="service-area-section">
		<div class="area-container">
			<h2 class="area-title">Serving Central Kentucky & Beyond</h2>
			<p class="area-subtitle">Based in Lexington. Focused on Central Kentucky. Capable of working anywhere.</p>

			<div class="area-content">
				<div class="area-text">
					<p>
						We're based in Lexington, Kentucky. We know this city. We understand its business culture, its opportunities, and its challenges. Our network is here. Our roots are here.
					</p>
					<p>
						Most of our clients are Central Kentucky businesses‚ÄîLexington, Frankfort, Richmond, Winchester, and surrounding areas. We've become known for delivering results for local businesses.
					</p>
					<p>
						But we also work with businesses beyond Kentucky. In today's digital world, geography is less important. We've built relationships with clients across the US because quality work travels.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="area-focus">
					<h3>We specialize in serving:</h3>
					<ul class="area-list">
						<li>Startups & new ventures launching in Lexington</li>
						<li>Service-based businesses (contractors, consultants, pros)</li>
						<li>Local retail & e-commerce</li>
						<li>Professional services (legal, accounting, real estate)</li>
						<li>Nonprofits & community organizations</li>
						<li>Established businesses ready to scale</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<section class="about-cta">
		<div class="cta-content">
			<h2 class="cta-title">Let's Work Together</h2>
			<p class="cta-description">Whether you need a website, marketing strategy, consulting, or just want to chat about your business goals, we'd love to connect.</p>
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<button class="cta-primary">Book a Discovery Call</button>
				<button class="cta-secondary">Get in Touch</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</RootLayout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.about-hero {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 50vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		overflow: hidden;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	.cosmic-background {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.stars {
		position: absolute;
		width: 2px;
		height: 2px;
		background: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		box-shadow: 100px 100px white, 200px 150px white, 300px 50px white, 450px 200px white,
					550px 100px white, 150px 300px white, 400px 400px white, 600px 300px white,
					700px 150px white, 800px 400px white, 900px 250px white, 200px 500px white,
					700px 500px white, 500px 600px white, 100px 700px white, 800px 700px white,
					300px 800px white;
		animation: twinkle 3s infinite;
	}


	.nebula {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		filter: blur(80px);
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.nebula-1 {
		width: 400px;
		height: 400px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
		top: 10%;
		left: 10%;
		animation: drift 8s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.nebula-2 {
		width: 500px;
		height: 500px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(163, 0, 255, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
		top: 50%;
		right: 5%;
		animation: drift 10s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
	}

	.nebula-3 {
		width: 350px;
		height: 350px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
		bottom: 10%;
		left: 50%;
		animation: drift 12s ease-in-out infinite;
	}


	.particles {
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.particles::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		width: 2px;
		height: 2px;
		background: var(--primary-neon);
		border-radius: 50%;
		box-shadow: 100px 200px var(--primary-neon), 250px 100px var(--primary-neon),
					150px 400px var(--secondary-neon), 450px 150px var(--tertiary-neon),
					600px 250px var(--primary-neon), 350px 300px var(--secondary-neon),
					800px 100px var(--tertiary-neon), 200px 600px var(--primary-neon);
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}


	.hero-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 900px;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		animation: fade-in-up 1s ease-out;
	}

	.about-headline {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-neon), var(--secondary-neon), var(--tertiary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.about-subheadline {
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		max-width: 700px;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}


	/* Mission Section */
	.mission-section {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.mission-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.mission-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.mission-card {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
		border: 2px solid var(--primary-neon);
		border-radius: 16px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.mission-card:hover {
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
		box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
		transform: translateY(-8px);
	}

	.mission-title {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: var(--primary-neon);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.mission-text {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.values-list {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.2rem;
	}

	.values-list li {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.values-list strong {
		color: var(--primary-neon);
	}

	/* Story Section */
	.story-section {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.story-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.story-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-neon), var(--primary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.story-content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.story-content p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	/* Beliefs Section */
	.beliefs-section {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.beliefs-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.beliefs-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tertiary-neon), var(--secondary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.beliefs-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.belief-item {
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
		border-radius: 14px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.belief-item:hover {
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.12);
		border-color: var(--primary-neon);
		transform: translateY(-8px);
	}

	.belief-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.belief-item p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* Team Section */
	.team-section {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.team-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.team-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-neon), var(--tertiary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.team-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.team-info {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.team-info p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	/* Process Section */
	.process-section {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.process-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.process-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-neon), var(--primary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.process-steps {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.process-step {
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
		border-radius: 14px;
		text-align: center;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.process-step:hover {
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.12);
		border-color: var(--primary-neon);
		transform: translateY(-8px);
	}

	.step-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.process-step h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.process-step p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* Service Area Section */
	.service-area-section {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.area-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.area-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tertiary-neon), var(--primary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.area-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.area-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.area-text {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.area-text p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.area-focus {
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
		border: 2px solid var(--primary-neon);
		border-radius: 14px;
	}

	.area-focus h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--primary-neon);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.area-list {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.area-list li {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.area-list li::before {
		content: '>';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--primary-neon);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	/* CTA Section */
	.about-cta {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
		min-height: 400px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.cta-content {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 700px;
	}

	.cta-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-neon), var(--secondary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.cta-description {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-hero {
			min-height: 40vh;
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.mission-section,
		.story-section,
		.beliefs-section,
		.team-section,
		.process-section,
		.service-area-section,
		.about-cta {
			padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.mission-grid,
		.beliefs-grid,
		.area-content {
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1rem;
		}
	}

